OL,3,CPlaid Cymru pledges extra childcare
OL,4,Cand lower NHS waiting lists if elected
OL,6,FPlaid Cymru's leader Rhun ap Iorwerth
OL,7,Fsays his party would aim to "get the
OL,8,Fbasics right" rather than "sort out
OL,9,Fevery problem" facing Wales if it
OL,10,Fleads the Welsh Government after May's
OL,11,FSenedd election.
OL,13,FWith polling suggesting that Plaid
OL,14,FCymru could be the largest party after
OL,15,Fthe election, the leader has today
OL,16,Fpublished the steps it would take in
OL,17,Fthe first hundred days of government,
OL,18,Fshould it be in that position.
OL,26,@pD@[OUqD@NO]
