PN,46602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1772457071
OL,3,CPlaid Cymru pledges extra childcare
OL,4,Cand lower NHS waiting lists if elected
OL,6,FAt the party's conference in Newport,
OL,7,Fhe published a document listing
OL,8,Factions including trying to rebuild
OL,9,Ftrust in the way that government works
OL,10,Fby strengthening a Welsh cabinet
OL,11,Foffice and appointing a dedicated
OL,12,Fminister.
OL,14,FWhen it comes to powers, a Plaid Cymru
OL,15,Fgovernment would argue for the
OL,16,Ftransfer to Wales of the same powers
OL,17,Fas Scotland, in a new Government of
OL,18,FWales Bill and establishing a standing
OL,19,F"National Commission" to decide what
OL,20,Fpowers Wales needs.
OL,26,@{D@AOU{D@UO]
