OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1772457071
OL,3,CPlaid Cymru pledges extra childcare
OL,4,Cand lower NHS waiting lists if elected
OL,6,FIn the area of health, the promise
OL,7,Fincludes action to bring NHS waiting
OL,8,Flists down including commissioning an
OL,9,Findependent review on NHS performance,
OL,10,Fpreparing a cancer plan for Wales and
OL,11,Fsetting up a "health finance
OL,12,Fefficiency team" to try to deal with
OL,13,Foverspends.
OL,15,FThe party says it would expand
OL,16,Fprovision of free childcare to 20
OL,17,Fhours for all 2 year olds and make
OL,18,Fmoves to tackle child poverty
OL,19,Fincluding piloting a Welsh Child
OL,20,FPayment known as Cynnal.
OL,26,@sD@NOUtD@PO]
