OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1772457071
OL,3,CPlaid Cymru pledges extra childcare
OL,4,Cand lower NHS waiting lists if elected
OL,6,FIn schools there would be a new
OL,7,Fliteracy and numeracy plan and the
OL,8,Froll out plans for libraries in all
OL,9,Fprimary schools. There'd be a review
OL,10,Fof how universities in Wales are
OL,11,Ffunded.
OL,13,FAmong the plans for the economy are a
OL,14,Fpromise to develop a new National
OL,15,FDevelopment Agency, a town centres
OL,16,Ftask force and a proposal to create a
OL,17,Fsingle energy company for Wales.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/7
