OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1772457071
OL,3,CPlaid Cymru pledges extra childcare
OL,4,Cand lower NHS waiting lists if elected
OL,6,F"People in Wales have increasingly
OL,7,Flost faith in governments ` they are
OL,8,Fseen as distant, not reflecting their
OL,9,Fpriorities, telling not listening,
OL,10,Ftalking not doing. We set out our new
OL,11,Fapproach as a government ` to bring
OL,12,Four public services together as One
OL,13,FWelsh Public Service and establish
OL,14,Fcore values that will drive our all
OL,15,Fwork."
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@FO]
