PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1772457071
OL,3,CPlaid Cymru pledges extra childcare
OL,4,Cand lower NHS waiting lists if elected
OL,6,FThe plan has been criticised by
OL,7,Fpolitical opponents. A Welsh Labour
OL,8,Fspokesperson said that, "This is a
OL,9,Fplan for cuts. Rhun just won't tell
OL,10,Fyou exactly where and when. All while
OL,11,Festablishing a commission to look to
OL,12,Fdrag us out of the UK making every
OL,13,Fsingle person poorer. They say they're
OL,14,Fgoing to be transparent, but there's
OL,15,Fnot much honesty here."
OL,26,@pD@YOUwD@WO]
